# A tibble: 694 x 2
    Variable                   Description                                      
    <chr>                      <chr>                                            
  1 Requeue_Flag_pOOBAH        Flag to automatically requeue a faild sample bas~
  2 Requeue_Flag_PnegEcdf      Flag to automatically requeue a faild sample bas~
  3 Sentrix_Name               Unique Sentrix Name: Sentrix_Barcode + Sentrix_P~
  4 Sentrix_Barcode            Sentrix Bar Code (AKA Sentrix_ID).               
  5 Sentrix_Poscode            Sentrix Position Code (AKA Sentrix_Position).    
  6 Sentrix_Row                Sentrix Row on chip.                             
  7 Sentrix_Col                Sentrix Column on Chip.                          
  8 Chip_Type                  Idat Chip Type.                                  
  9 Chip_Format                Idat Chip Format (e.g. 8x1/12x1/24x1/etc.).      
 10 Bead_Pool                  Automatically identified bead pool based on addr~

 20 Bead_Total_ch              Total number of sample ch# bead-types found over~
